Package org.ggp.base.util.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CloseableTabs  
    ConsolePanel
    ConsolePanel implements a light-weight panel that shows all of the messages being send to stdout and stderr.
    GameSelector
    GameSelector is a pair of widgets for selecting a game repository and then choosing a game from that game repository.
    GameStateRenderer
    GameStateRenderer generates an image that represents the current state of a match, based on the current state of the match (in XML) and an XSLT that converts that XML match state into HTML.
    GameStateRenderer.IOString  
    JLabelBold  
    JLabelHyperlink  
    NativeUI
    NativeUI is a simple user-interface wrapper around the snippet of code that configures the Java UI to adopt the look-and-feel of the operating system that it's running on.
